          "id": 794465,
          "name": "Meta Description",
          "value": "The Position\nCallRail is seeking a curious and adaptable Product Designer to join one of our Core Products teams. In this role, you'll work on the features and flows that sit at the heart of the CallRail platform—across integrations, billing, and attribution—designing experiences that are clear, reliable, and genuinely useful for small businesses.\n\nYou'll be embedded across our integrations, billing, and attribution teams, partnering closely with Product Managers, engineers, and fellow designers to solve real customer problems and ship great work. We lean heavily into AI tools like Gemini and Claude as part of how we design and prototype—you'll be expected to use them throughout your process, from early exploration through handoff.\n\nThis role is a great fit for someone who brings a positive, inquisitive attitude above all else, loves to prototype and experiment quickly, and is energized by a team that invests in your growth and celebrates your success.",
          "value_type": "long_text"
        }
      ],
